  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA348-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu vēṭkai perukat tāṅkallāḷāy (EN, ER: tāṅkalāḷāy; ET: tāṅkakilaḷāy) āṟṟāmai mītūrkiṉṟāḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what she who surpresses [her] incapacity said as one who could not endure when desire increased.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA348">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            nilavē, nīṉiṟa vicumpiṟ palkatir parappip</l>
<l>            pāṉmali kaṭaliṟ parantupaṭ ṭaṉṟē</l>
<l>            yūrē, yolivaruñ cummaiyoṭu maliputoku pīṇṭik</l>
<l>            kalikeḻu maṟukiṉ viḻavaya rummē</l>
<l>            kāṉē, pūmalar kañaliya poḻilakan tōṟun</l>
<l>            tāmamar tuṇaiyoṭu vaṇṭimi rummē</l>
<l>            yāṉē, puṉaiyiḻai ñekiḻtta pulampuko ḷavalamoṭu</l>
<l>            kaṉaiyiruṅ kaṅkuluṅ kaṇpaṭai yileṉē, yataṉā</l>
<l>            leṉṉoṭu poruṅkoliv vulaka</l>
<l>            mulakamoṭu poruṅkoleṉ ṉavalamuṟu neñcē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent4">            The moonlight,</l>
<l rend="indent">            spreading [its] many rays in the blue-coloured sky</l>
<l>        it has expanded<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">parantu paṭṭaṉṟu</term>: presumably <term xml:lang="ta">paṭu</term> as an auxiliary adds here a nuance of Unwillkuerlichkeit, which, in contradistinction to <term xml:lang="ta">taru</term> in this function has not the connotation of a powerful force behind it, but rather something that seems to happen all by itself.</note> like the great milk ocean.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            The village,</l>
<l rend="indent">            crowding, gathering happily, with the burden of noise increasing,</l>
<l>        is engaged in a festival in the bustling streets.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            The forest,</l>
<l rend="indent">            inside every grove dense with flowers blossoming</l>
<l>        bees are humming with the companions they desire.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            I,</l>
<l rend="indent">            with the affliction brought by loneliness that made loose [my]</l>
<l rend="indent">             decorative jewels</l>
<l>        even in the full dark of night I do not sleep.</l>
<l>        Therefore, does this world make war on me?</l>
<l>        Does my afflicted heart make war on this world?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
